<br>
&quot;How dare she do this to me?&quot;<br>
<br>
The young dark elf smiled at one of the puny Sisters of Erollisi Marr.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ahh, I feel much better now!&quot; he sang as he brought his shield up in preparation for the wood elf's charge.<br>
<br>
&quot;I was weak.  Vulnerable.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll teach you to mess with me!&quot; shouted the Sister, crashing her halberd down on his shield.  The impact was strong and jarred Shiden backwards, but he managed to stay upright.<br>
<br>
&quot;I did it as a service.  To repay the debt of kindness.&quot;<br>
<br>
Shiden glared at the Sister and a thick cloud of disease formed around her, forcing her to bend over and cough.<br>
<br>
&quot;Who are,&quot; she tried to say between coughs, &quot;you talking to?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Innoruuk, guide me!&quot;<br>
<br>
Shiden brought the large shield in a wide arc, aimed right for the wood elf woman's temple, but she deftly knocked the shield aside with her halberd and lunged in towards him.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> You did it yourself.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
A cry of pain leapt from the shadowknight's throat as the halberd dug deep into his thigh.  The Sister, unprepared to actually score a hit, looked up at him for half a second with blind shock in her eyes.<br>
<br>
&quot;Fine.  I did it myself.  What of it?&quot;<br>
<br>
Shiden peeled the bloody purity belt off of the wood elf's body and picked up his red-bathed axe.  He looked down at the wood elf and almost felt sorry for what he had done, since it was not her fault that She had happened to him.  She was to blame.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> No, not Her.  Just you.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Just me,&quot; Shiden said as he went to wash his axe in the ocean. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=286.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=286.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=286.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=286.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=286.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=286.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm58">Telegrams!<option value="firionaviefrm47">Guilds and Associations<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Day<option value="firionaviefrm23">Hero Heart Tavern<option value="firionaviefrm15">The Polling Booth<option value="firionaviefrm40">Kudos!<option value="